<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
		<script src="../../script/flexible_css.js"></script>
		<script src="../../script/flexible.js"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/api.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/commonWindow.css" />
		<title>加微信好友</title>
		<style type="text/css">
			div{
				white-space: nowrap;
			}
			body,html{
				background-color: #f5f5f5;
			}
			#topbar{
				box-shadow:0 1px 0 0 #f2f2f2;
			}
			.fit{
				box-sizing: border-box;
				padding: 0 0.4rem;
			}
			.friend_info{
				box-sizing: border-box;
				height: 1.866666rem;
				width: 100%;
				background-color: white;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				padding-left: 0.4rem;
				position: relative;
				margin-top: 0.026666rem;
			}
			.friend_info_head{
				width: 1.226666rem;
				height: 1.226666rem;
				background-color: pink;
				border-radius: 100%;
			}
			.friend_info_id{
				height: 0.533333rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color:#333333;
				position: absolute;
				left: 1.866666rem;
				top: 0.666666rem;
			}
			.selled{
				height: 0.453333rem;
				position: absolute;
				right: 0.4rem;
				top: 0.72rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.32rem;
				color:#ff5c98;
			}
			.price{
				box-sizing: border-box;
				height: 2.666666rem;
				width: 100%;
				background-color: white;
				margin-top: 0.026666rem;
				padding-top: 0.32rem;
				padding-left: 0.4rem;
				position: relative;
			}
			.lie{
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color:#333333;
			}
			.money{
				margin-top: 0.64rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color:#333333;
			}
			.count{
				position: absolute;
				top: 1.386666rem;
				left: 50%;
				width: 1.946666rem;
				height: 0.746666rem;
				margin-left: -0.973333rem;
				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color: #999999;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
			}
			.count>b{
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Bold;
				font-size: 0.533333rem;
				color:#ff5c98;
			}
			.wallet{
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				width: 100%;
				height: 1.706666rem;
				background-color: white;
				margin-top: 0.026666rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color: #999999;
				position: relative;
			}
			.wallet>div{
				display: inline-block;
			}
			.wallet_count{
				margin-left: 0.32rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
s				font-size: 0.373333rem;
				color:#333333;
			}
			.recharge{
				background:#ff5c98;
				border-radius: 0.106666rem;
				width: 1.226666rem;
				height: 0.64rem;
				position: relative;
				color: white;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 0.64rem;
				left: 0.266666rem;
			}
			.tips{
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				padding-top: 0.32rem;
				padding-left: 0.2rem;
				font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
				font-size: 0.32rem;
				color:#999999;
			}
			.loginButton{
				width: 8.666666rem;
				margin: 0 auto;
				margin-top: 4.72rem;
				color: #fff;
				background-image:linear-gradient(-227deg, #fe4f8a 13%,#ff77a9  87%);
				font-size: 0.48rem;
				height: 1.173333rem;
				border-radius: 0.586666rem;
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
	
    <div class="friend_info fit">
    	<div class="friend_info_head"></div>
    	<div class="friend_info_id">请叫我妲姬</div>
    	<div class="selled">已售20单</div>
    </div>
    <div class="price fit">
    	<div class="lie">已开通微信加好友，机会难得，赶紧下手吧</div>
    	<div class="money">价格</div>
    	<div class="count"><b>1200</b>  LB</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wallet fit">
    	<div class="title">
    		账户余额
    	</div>
    	<div class="wallet_count">0.0LB</div>
    	<div class="recharge" tapmode="itemOn" onclick="openRechargeWin()">充值</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tips fit">
    	购买你可以获得微信号，加女神为好友，就可以尽情撩她了<br/>
		如女神3天内未通过你的好友申请，将全额退款
    </div>
    <div class="loginButton flex flex-align-center flex-pack-center">立即支付</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakooLib/QuakooBase-1.0.0.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakooLib/QuakooConfig-1.0.0.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakooLib/QuakooBaseApp-1.0.0.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakooLib/QuakooBaseAppBusiness-1.0.0.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakoo/Config.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../script/api.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/script/quakoo/project.js"></script>
		<script>
			apiready = function() {
				
			};
			//打开充值窗口
			 function openRechargeWin() {
        		quakooApp.openNewWindow('recharge','../mine/recharge.html',{})
   			 }
		</script>
	</body>

</html>